# Launcher scripts — preserve exact bytes. The .bat are ASCII wrappers that call the
# matching .ps1; the .ps1 hold the Persian UI and are UTF-8 WITH BOM (Windows
# PowerShell 5.1 needs the BOM to read the Persian correctly) with CRLF endings.
# Marked binary so git never applies line-ending/encoding normalization.
*.bat -text
*.ps1 -text
